name: J Castro M.
description:
This is a leather bucket bag from J Castro M. 
 The bag is brown and features a drawstring closure on top and embossed pictures of cattle, carts, and a farmhouse all around it. 
 It measures about 8 wide, 7.75 tall, and 5 deep 
 This bag comes in good pre-owned condition with some tears on each side seam of the top half of the bag. The bag is being sold for repair
